PrecisEnactment of the INDIAN TIMBER HARVESTING REGULATIONS which (a) provide that anyone who cuts timber on first nation reserve lands or surrendered lands obtain a licence to do so, and (b) repeal the Stuart-Trembleur Lake Band (Tanizul Timber Ltd.) Timber Regulations.
